snippet.title: Furina Teaser 「Member of the Cast」 Piano Performance / Genshin Impact OST
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact - Furina Teaser 「Member of the Cast」 OST Piano Performance


Today's performance is "Furina" Teaser theme "Member of the Cast"
The Hydro Archon has finally appeared in Pickup in the New Continent of Fontaine!

She appears as a pickup in the first half of version 4.2
She was also a character who seemed to have a lot of secrets.
The PV also hints at various things with a subtle atmosphere.

In particular, this PV is outstanding in many ways, including dialogue, directing, and effects.
It has such an amazing atmosphere and feel, I was really impressed.
The music is also excellent, and it is by far the best among the Fontaine character tracks.

This performance was based on my fellow piano arrangement content creator 'CC Music' with some modifications

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
Nilou's 'Dance of Sabzeruz' Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/Ab97Db-3FiU
Aranara's Theme Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/YJtCY1zp94Y
'Dori' theme Insane Piano Duet Performance : https://youtu.be/7gAj7fL8edg
Collei Demo 「Sprout in the Thicket」 Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/4_P8vIO2EXI

템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
